    dc:description "Figures 2, 3. Lateral view of larval head and thoracic segments. 2. Penestola bufalis (Guenee, 1854) (NMNH); 3. Penestola wichardi Solis, Leger, and Neumann, sp. nov., holotype (MfN)." ;
